data.description: Welcome home to this wonderful, open concept 2 Story Townhome centrally located within minutes of shopping, amenities, and local parks. This home offers just over 1,670 finished square feet of living space which includes 2 Bedrooms (1 on the main floor and 1 on the upper level), a large Living Room with Vaulted Ceilings and gas Fireplace, a Nook for an eating table, a good sized Kitchen with pantry and access to the rear fenced in yard with a huge Deck. Upstairs you'll find laminate floors throughout, a large Loft that is currently used as an office/second TV room with its own Balcony off the back, the Main Bedroom with it's own Ensuite that includes a Whirlpool Tub, plenty of great closet space and tons of natural light. Some of the recent upgrades include brand new windows, a new front entry door, a freshly painted exterior, and some soft touches inside throughout the home. This home has been well kept and is ready for it's new owners. Call today for your showing.
